- **MIDI-Emotion Research**: Computational Aesthetics in Music
- **Cross-Cultural Aesthetics**: Avoiding Western Bias in AI Systems (Rhue, 2023)
- **Ethics of Emotionally Creative AI**: Implications and Responsibilities (Stark & Hoey, 2021)
- **Measurement Frameworks**: Validating Cathartic Resolution in AI Systems

